INTRODUCTION

    "Unix Way" (or "Linux Way") is to combine several simple tools into
    complex one necessary to solve the problem. Sometimes one needs tool
    to repeatedly respawn some application after it's termination. The
    "respawn" tool is for that purpose.


Version 2 - "keep alive" mode

    Sometimes one needs to respawn buggy program but only if it crashes.


